Global Polio Eradication Initiative update as of 17 Oct 2012
---------------------------------------------
Total cases
Year-to-date 2012 / Year-to-date 2011 / Total in 2011*
Globally: 177 / 467 / 650
- in endemic countries: 166 / 196 / 341
- in non-endemic countries: 5 / 271 / 309

Case breakdown by country
